      "text": "The FBI is committed to keeping our communities safe and we're working every day to accomplish this mission.\n\nThis morning, FBI Minneapolis, with support from federal, state, and local law enforcement partners, conducted court-authorized law enforcement activity as part of an ongoing federal criminal investigation. \n\nWe encourage members of the public to remain vigilant and report anything they consider suspicious to law enforcement immediately, call their local FBI office, or submit information to https://t.co/N0nXE2oZYg.\n\nThe FBI values our partnerships with law enforcement and the public to prevent, detect, and deter crime.",
      "text_resolved": "The FBI is committed to keeping our communities safe and we're working every day to accomplish this mission.\n\nThis morning, FBI Minneapolis, with support from federal, state, and local law enforcement partners, conducted court-authorized law enforcement activity as part of an ongoing federal criminal investigation. \n\nWe encourage members of the public to remain vigilant and report anything they consider suspicious to law enforcement immediately, call their local FBI office, or submit information to http://tips.fbi.gov.\n\nThe FBI values our partnerships with law enforcement and the public to prevent, detect, and deter crime.",
